description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for highly motivated and enthusiastic qualified nurses to work in our Integrated Medical Specialties Care Group. To succeed in this role you will need to be able to work autonomously, and in addition provide a positive contribution to #TeamCDDFT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a motivated, enthusiastic nurse, with good communication skills you will have the opportunity to extend those skills with a range of learning opportunities provided by the trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are interested in receiving applications from nurses interested in the following specialties:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Emergency Medicine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care of the Elderly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stroke&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cardiology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Respiratory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rheumatology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diabetes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gastroenterology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vacancies are subject to current availability&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A date for your diary&lt;/strong&gt; - interviews scheduled monthly with the &lt;strong&gt;next round on 25thNovember 2020. Please note that these interview will be conducted remotely.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
